dnl
dnl A dummy source file for trivial compiler tests.
dnl This is only useful for AC_COMPILE_IFLSE because it doesn't link.  
dnl
dnl @category Cxx
dnl @version 2006-05-08
dnl @author David Fang <fangism@users.sourceforge.net>
